{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji22.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致王震电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致王震电山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年8月17日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们希望你率所部进至陇南后，即在两当、徽县一带分散游击，建立陇南游击根据地，对于目前牵制敌人，帮助五师及粉碎蒋介石向整个解放区进攻，帮助必大。对于将来我军向南发展则是一准备步骤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致王震电的主要内容。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":8,"day":17}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":79,"page_end":79},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"王震","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}